          "en": "Google DeepMind introduced a cognitive framework to measure progress toward AGI, while Microsoft Research launched AgentRx for systematic debugging of AI agents.",
          "zh": "Google DeepMind推出了一项衡量通用人工智能进展的认知框架，而微软研究院发布了AgentRx以实现对人工智能智能体的系统调试。"
        },
        "key_takeaways": {
          "en": [
