            "AI agents are transitioning from simple chatbots to systems capable of handling cloud incidents, navigating complex web interfaces, and executing multi-step API workflows."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "Google DeepMind的框架旨在量化通用人工智能的进展，并通过Kaggle黑客马拉松支持评估开发。",
